title: Trump and Netanyahu to meet in Florida at a crucial moment for the Gaza ceasefire
description: President Trump could use the face-to-face at his Mar-a-Lago estate to look for ways to speed up the peace process, as Israel's leader has been accused of not pushing his side to move fast enough.
